{"tid":894703,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人 一多人就會驚，不安？","createTime":"2018-11-08T14:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T17:15:32.000Z","uid":208916,"like":90,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e58f56efb1ef3273fd0c26e40494ddcf4ec51649","tid":894703,"uid":208916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:47:38.000Z","msg":"返學嗰度好多人來來往往，迎面而來就會驚。<br />\n一行過呢啲地方就會驚，內心感覺「抖唔到氣」，想快啲逃離現場。<br />\n<br />\n如果同班唔熟朋友一齊，都係好驚，今日同佢哋食飯 ，個頭好暈 ，好驚 ，個人想縮埋一舊，好想食快啲，可以快啲走，然後可以自己一個返屋企。<br />\n<br />\n想問呢啲係咪有病？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n表面唔會表現出嚟，但內心驚到癡線。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b5885dc98afcc79a3d9fc55b724c37d7c698cf","tid":894703,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:48:30.000Z","msg":"社交焦慮"},{"pid":"0830816ff68f200a857fc59ae778931950e81ccb","tid":894703,"uid":106133,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:51:15.000Z","msg":"揮手 解決方案係唔好將自己放大 同打少啲飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e4a8bf5d02b6c09d4f49d166cee74305f9f950","tid":894703,"uid":208916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0830816ff68f200a857fc59ae778931950e81ccb","tid":894703,"uid":106133,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:51:15.000Z","msg":"揮手 解決方案係唔好將自己放大 同打少啲飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:03:14.000Z","msg":"真絲。"},{"pid":"211350ebc3c45a6eea2ed9c1ade42e80b213d37d","tid":894703,"uid":208916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0830816ff68f200a857fc59ae778931950e81ccb","tid":894703,"uid":106133,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:51:15.000Z","msg":"揮手 解決方案係唔好將自己放大 同打少啲飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:04:24.000Z","msg":"好驚人啊  成日一經過一堆frd ，姐係幾個人一齊行嗰